:"text","value":"Incidents can take the form of ‚Äúmicroaggressions,‚Äù which is a damaging form of harassment. Microaggressions are the everyday slights or insults which communicate negative messages to target individuals, often based upon their marginalized group membership. Over time, microaggressions can take a great toll on mental and emotional health, and the target‚Äôs feeling of belonging in science and academia. The following examples can all be labeled micro-aggressions:","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"Vpvuryubnu"},{"type":"break","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"pG6JNLQT5K"},{"type":"text","value":"‚õî Commenting on a woman‚Äôs appearance rather than her work;","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"fSgYjyp2zN"},{"type":"break","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"tPyou9efSB"},{"type":"text","value":"‚õî Only directing questions at male colleagues when there are female experts in the room;","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"MfmZPkF35O"},{"type":"break","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"iHIgLVLo8J"},{"type":"text","value":"‚õî Telling someone of colour that they ‚Äúspeak such good English‚Äù;","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"wXLS12UpHy"},{"type":"break","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"XFuAmej0Ne"},{"type":"text","value":"‚õî Forcefully praising meat to an individual with a vegetarian diet;","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"r5k5pBp45q"},{"type":"break","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"Uyg6lFyxPr"},{"type":"text","value":"‚õî Praising alcoholic drinks to an individual who do not consume them.","position":